```
┌─ GET /api/users/42 ─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Status:   200 OK                                       │
│  Time:     23.4ms                                       │
│  Request Headers:                                       │
│    Authorization: Bearer ***...***                      │
│    Content-Type:  application/json                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

